  m_sTitle "Overview"
  m_sTextData "CDF assaults open fields and fortified russian positions."
  m_bEmptyFactionVisibility 1
  m_bShowForAnyFaction 1
  m_iOrder 10
 }
 {
  coords -7085.485 159.547 4642.831
  m_sTitle "Mission Notes"
  m_sTextData "End conditions:"\
  ""\
  "Farm Captured: CDF Victory"\
  "90% RU casualties: CDF Victory"\
  ""\
  "90% CDF casualties: RU Victory"\
  "70 minute time limit: RU Victory"
  m_bEmptyFactionVisibility 1
  m_bShowForAnyFaction 1
  m_iOrder 15
 }
 {
  coords 7535.767 164.567 4383.896
  m_sTitle "Lore"
  m_sTextData "The Russian Federation launched a full invasion of the Republic of Chernarus after years of border pressure and false territorial claims. The Chernarussian Defense Forces are defending their homeland against a larger invading army."\
  ""\
  ""\
  "The war has become a long south-to-north front, with both sides fighting over roads, towns, and high ground. The Chotain sector is one small but important part of that larger front. Russian forces currently hold the farms west of Chotain. The farms sit on high ground and provide observation over nearby roads and approaches."\
  ""\
  ""\
  "If the Russians keep the farms, they can control movement through the area and protect their local supply line. CDF forces are attacking from the west, moving out from the Levie direction."\
  ""\
  ""\
  "Their goal is to retake the farms and push Russian forces off the high ground. Control of the farms could decide who holds the Chotain sector."
  m_bEmptyFactionVisibility 1
  m_bShowForAnyFaction 1
  m_iOrder 20
 }
}
